annotationA: Anaphase promoting complex subunit 4, isoform A; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: regulation of mitotic metaphase/anaphase transition; anaphase-promoting complex-dependent proteasomal ubiquitin-dependent protein catabolic process
annotationB: Anaphase-promoting complex subunit 10; Component of the anaphase promoting complex/cyclosome (APC/C), a cell cycle-regulated ubiquitin ligase that controls progression through mitosis and the G1 phase of the cell cycle
